{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/social-situations/job-loss-social-situation","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Job loss - social situation","meta_description":"What to do if it happens.","content":{"processed":"<p>The whole <strong>procedure of what to do </strong>was written by the Labour Office <a href=\"https://www.uradprace.cz/co-delat-pri-ztrate-zamestnani\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">on their website</a>. </p>\n<p>If you have <strong>returned from the EU/EEA/Switzerland</strong> where you terminated your employment, you can find information on what to do here.</p>\n<p>We wish you good luck and just to be safe we remind you that here on this site you will also find information about possible compensations, benefits and also where to seek professional psychological help if necessary</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/social-situations/job-loss-social-situation"},"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-10T16:47:54+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"work"},"situation_type":{"name":"Social situations","path":{"alias":"/situations/social-situations"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"people_alt"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Unemployment due to Covid-19","path":{"alias":"/situations/employment/unemployment-due-covid-19","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Impossibility to repay a loan or a mortgage - citizen","path":{"alias":"/situations/compensation/impossibility-repay-loan-or-mortgage-citizen","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":null,"last_updated":"2020-11-10T17:47:54+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Social situations","path":{"alias":"/situations/social-situations"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"people_alt"},"situation":[{"id":"8faac4a0-5038-57fc-bab9-980819f48b9e","title":"Grief and loss","path":{"alias":"/s